data.description:
Stunning Terrain home perfectly blending luxury and functionality. Upon entry you will be greeted with a flowing open
 concept adorned with new designer light fixtures among other finishes that are sure to impress. The entry way features a
 large living space and spacious main floor office/den is perfect for the family who works from home or needs space for
 hobbies. Entertaining is a joy with an expansive kitchen adorned with leathered granite counters, double oven, as well as
 endless prep space. The kitchen overlooks the sprawling living room and back patio with plumbed in gas grill. Finish your
 day upstairs in the luxurious primary suite complete with his and hers closets. The upstairs also features 3 more bedrooms
 with walk in closets and full bath with double sinks, as well as newer carpet in all bedrooms. The full basement has been
 partially finished complete with family room, bedroom (non-conforming), and full bath. The unfinished space is perfect for
 the home gym or storage. Enjoy the outdoors and everything the Terrain has to offer when you call this one home! Prime
 location within walking distance to award winning Sage Canyon Elementary, trails, parks, and dog park. Neighborhood also
 features 2 pools! The Terrain is located in the heart of the Castle Rock community and everything it has to offer. Enjoy the
 stylish and comfortable luxuries when you call this home! Virtual and 3D tour https://western-exposures-photography.aryeo.com/sites/3643-golden-spur-loop-castle-rock-co-80108-4121901/branded
